  "concepts": [
    "Spanish nouns have gender: masculine (el) or feminine (la)",
    "Many -o words are masculine, many -a words are feminine",
    "Words ending in -dad and -ción are almost always feminine",
    "El = the (masculine), La = the (feminine)"
  ],
